## üì• How to Download Oracle VirtualBox ##
1. Visit the Official VirtualBox Website

Go to the official download page:

üëâ https://www.virtualbox.org

2. Select ‚ÄúDownload VirtualBox‚Äù

On the homepage, click Download VirtualBox to open the downloads section.

3. Choose Your Operating System

Under VirtualBox Platform Packages, select the installer for your OS:

Windows hosts ‚Äì for Windows 10/11

macOS hosts ‚Äì for Mac

Linux distributions ‚Äì for Ubuntu, Debian, etc.

Example (Windows):
Click Windows hosts to start the download.

4. Download the Installer

A file similar to one of the following will download:
VirtualBox-7.x.x-Win.exe      # Windows
VirtualBox-7.x.x-macOS.dmg    # macOS
VirtualBox-7.x.x-Linux.run    # Linux

5. Run the Installer

Windows: Double-click the .exe file

macOS: Open the .dmg file and drag VirtualBox into Applications

Linux: Run the .run file with terminal permissions

6. Complete the Installation

Follow the installation wizard:

Click Next through the prompts

Allow any permissions or driver installations

Click Install

Click Finish to open VirtualBox
